subtitle: I am studying software development and mobile app development at Fontys University of Applied Sciences in Eindhoven
about_me: I study at Fontys in Eindhoven in the 4th semester, where I chose the software development track. At the moment, I'm focusing on mobile app development, and I'm also learning more about UI and UX design. I enjoy working on projects where I can quickly see the results and impact of my work.
